#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/12/
msgid "[[Goldrinn, the Great Wolf||59955]] + [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]] and [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] gives a huge aura affect to all beasts you summon. Usually, you want to taunt and reborn the Goldrinn so the Macaw always procs it and it always dies. [[Sewer Lord||130996]] is the best summon beast to run in this comp."
msgstr "[[Goldrinn, the Great Wolf||59955]] + [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]] 和 [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] 会为所有你召唤的野兽提供强大的光环效果。通常你需要让戈德林获得嘲讽和复生，这样鹦鹉就能持续触发该效果，而戈德林也会不断死亡。[[Sewer Lord||130996]] 是该流派中最佳的野兽召唤选择。"

